                    <span>I didn't find this book terribly interesting, whereas I found Andrew S. Tanenbaum's Computer Networks _very_interesting.  I'd advise checking out Tanenbaum in addition (or instead of ) to checking out this book!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Wants to learn networks?  This is the book for you!</div>
